reviewText: One disc is the correct region, one is not.

I love these movies, but please note that although the 2 Blu-ray pack is labeled as "Region: All Regions", only the first movie works on my US blu-ray player. The second movie gives an area code error.
Fantastic movies. Love Dani Rovira and Clara Lago.
These DVDs do not work in Australia. This should be clearly stated. Orders should not be accepted or shipped to Australia.
